headline: Is It Too Late To Consider C.H. Robinson Worldwide (CHRW) After A 70% One-Year Rally?
summary: If you are wondering whether C.H. Robinson Worldwide at around US$177.90 is offering good value right now, it helps to break the story into what the share price has done and what the fundamentals might justify. The stock has recently recorded returns of 1.5% over 7 days, 8.1% over 30 days, 8.7% year to date, 69.9% over 1 year, 96.8% over 3 years and 125.1% over 5 years, which naturally raises questions about how much of that performance is already reflected in the current price.
